title: Dead Kennedys - Frankenchrist
description:
This is the third album by the American hardcore punk band Dead Kennedys. Released in 1985 on the Alternative Tentacles Label, founded by the frontman for Dead Kennedys, Jello Biafra. 

Frankchrist is musically different from Dead Kennedys' other albums. It's less raw punk; the songs are longer and with much more elaborate arrangement. The lyrics are significantly more focused and pointed. This is the album where they hit their stride. 

Note: This torrent is missing the second track titled "Untitled." This is because any work titled "Untitled" is an absolute bitch to find and I could not. I have never heard the song and am of the belief its absence does not interfere with the album.
